        <title>三角洲行动搬砖日常</title>
        <link>https://hugo-ap0.pages.dev/p/%E4%B8%89%E8%A7%92%E6%B4%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%8A%A8%E6%90%AC%E7%A0%96%E6%97%A5%E5%B8%B8/</link>
